{"tid":921921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴爾追隨C.朗轉投祖記？經理人曖昧表態...","createTime":"2018-11-30T03:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T08:54:40.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2315c7eea49d597743bdf28d0e396a8c6894919a","tid":921921,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"　　皇馬球星巴爾的經理人巴奈特29日被問到他的客戶是否會在未來轉會祖雲達斯，他的回答是「沒有不可能」。<br />\n<br />\n　　巴奈特表示，巴爾被認為是克&middot;朗拿度（C.朗拿度）離隊後皇馬的招牌球星之一，但巴爾也有可能追隨C.朗拿度的腳步加盟祖記。<br />\n<br />\n　　巴奈特說：「加雷斯（巴爾）在皇馬很開心，但是轉會市場是瞬息萬變的。C.朗拿度的離隊是皇馬的巨大損失，加雷斯很享受與C.朗拿度一起踢球，但加雷斯也很開心，因為他在一家頂級球會。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「在C.朗拿度加盟意甲之後，很多其他超級球星也都開始考慮意甲了，與前幾年相比他們對意甲的看法已經有所改變。」巴奈特說。"},{"pid":"19409fc291a83bfdc3de59667ba2bf9127171150","tid":921921,"uid":90863,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"跟尾狗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2fd1897d7894b576d522a66124b864cba6f1fa","tid":921921,"uid":221275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"克&middot;朗拿度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17391db4f36e96f72dfc8ef430c452f212be5aec","tid":921921,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"克&bull;朗拿度"},{"pid":"3198229c45a1f7c8c4d76e2fbfdcc8f88fc77330","tid":921921,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:08:35.000Z","msg":"之前仲串鳩牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a20ee9e33e1dca43d2062540d6d36392e682bf","tid":921921,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"金手指追到去祖度死牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c955deb20f7089986e5ce1f335520512978af5","tid":921921,"uid":64464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited